==Dutch==
===Etymology===
Note that the word only occurs in this diminutive form; the word "sprook" does not exist.

===Noun===
'''sprookje''' {{n}} (''plural:'' '''[[sprookjes]]''')
#A usually old, allegorical short story.
#Very pleasant situation.
#:''Sinds mijn huwelijk is mijn leven een sprookje.'' - ''Since my marriage my life has been a fairy tale.''
#Story that is not true.

